name: DECEIVE COIN
description:
These are the most Expensive used By Criss Angel in his performance.

All our custom made design and hand crafted and are to it’s precision.

These re-edged sets are truly something special! Kamran Khan suggested that I not only re-edge the inner coins, but the shell as well, that way everything would match perfectly. So that’s exactly what I did, while maintaining the same actual size of the coin with zero distortion! One of the benefits of this shell is that it sets almost all the way over the other coins..


The new edge also allows superior edge-gripping ability. This design works best with soft coins due to their smooth surfaces and superior edges. Many working pros have switched to this set. Criss Angel uses this set for his routines.

name: REVELATION SERVICE
description:
Revelation Service


For the first time in Pakistan Spirt Reading is been possible. Now you can see the words appear on a piece of paper in your own house, and all you needed was some water? Revelation Service makes it possible. All you do: concentrate on a thought. Imagine their glass of water as a crystal ball and to focus their thoughts into it. Dip the piece of paper into the water. Instantly, yet slowly and eerily, APPEARS ON THE PAPER!

 



All you need to do is provide us with a complete family details with D.O.B and little detail regarding the problem in hand. Please don't forget to write your full mailing address to send the Revelation Results in the post.



Revelation Service is not Black Magic, it is a tool help you finding the truth base upon the information is been provided by you. It is a tool that tells you what you need to do, It is a tool to provide you with the references for your protection.



Once we receive the payment you will be given a telephone number to call on

name: DECEIVE
description:
A card penetrates a ziploc bag, right before your eyes.

In life and in magic, there exists a line where the possible meets the impossible. There's a roadblock. A barrier. A limit. Deceive crosses that line and never looks back.

Here's what your spectator sees: a card is selected from any deck. It's a free choice-- no force. Signed. The card is then lost in the deck, then shuffled. The cards are then dribbled on top of a sealed Ziploc bag.

Slowly, the bag is lifted up from underneath the chaos of cards to show that one card is sealed INSIDE the bag-- the spectator's signed card.

name: THE DEVIL
description:
The spectator thinks of anything. A name. A number. A memory. With the thought in mind, the spectator squeezes your wrist. Tightly.

Can be performed impromptu, and surrounded.
Reveal a name, a number, a card.... anything you can think of.
No gimmicks, props, setup, and no reset.
Taught step-by-step. No detail is left out.

name: ABUSE
description:
Now you can Abuses the laws of nature, allowing you to mysteriously and from a distance stop and start the flow of liquid from an innocent bottle of water while your spectator is holding it.

Prepare any bottle in 10 seconds 
Nothing to hide or get rid of... end clean 
Perform completely surrounded

Effect starts and ends in spectators hand.

Being able to do this with a clear water bottle that they can actually look up into and see the water suspended from is one of the big selling points of the effect.
